    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><u>Serve Customers with a smile</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Serve as many customers as possible each day, ensuring you provide them with the correct medication. The more customers you satisfy, the better!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178890/extras/493cb62ca15e5a6c149be151e9450c74.avif?t=1761147747\" width=400 height=224 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><u>Look up medications and illnesses</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Use the GCD to research various medications and illnesses, then determine the best way to treat each customer's illness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178890/extras/b0d7f16f365087558b654232dc3f7a33.poster.avif?t=1761147747\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178890/extras/b0d7f16f365087558b654232dc3f7a33.webm?t=1761147747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178890/extras/b0d7f16f365087558b654232dc3f7a33.mp4?t=1761147747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><u>Cut Pills into their specified dose</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Use the scissors to cut blister packs into their specified dose. Be sure to dispose of the waste!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178890/extras/9442a0dd785652a125da2c6b60299afe.poster.avif?t=1761147747\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178890/extras/9442a0dd785652a125da2c6b60299afe.webm?t=1761147747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178890/extras/9442a0dd785652a125da2c6b60299afe.mp4?t=1761147747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><u>Order and manage your stock</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Label and organise your stock to keep track of your medications. As your stock grows, so do your options - so stay organised!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178890/extras/54f11b595d121c9aa633ddf6266b3d55.poster.avif?t=1761147747\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178890/extras/54f11b595d121c9aa633ddf6266b3d55.webm?t=1761147747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178890/extras/54f11b595d121c9aa633ddf6266b3d55.mp4?t=1761147747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><u>Avoid costly mistakes</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Vitacure Pharmaceuticals expects perfection. Any mistakes will be punished with fines!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178890/extras/90eda9cfc6245cf2e8c13ba46b6e29c4.poster.avif?t=1761147747\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178890/extras/90eda9cfc6245cf2e8c13ba46b6e29c4.webm?t=1761147747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2178890/extras/90eda9cfc6245cf2e8c13ba46b6e29c4.mp4?t=1761147747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
